<header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title">School Closure Extended Through May 15</h1>
<div class="entry-meta"> Posted on <a href="https://www.chathamcentralschools.com/2020/04/16/school-closure-extended-through-may-15/" title="1:48 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2020-04-16T13:48:25-04:00">April 16, 2020</time></a><time class="updated" datetime="2020-04-17T09:44:50-04:00">April 17, 2020</time>
</div></header><div class="entry-content"><p>(April 16, 2020) Today, Governor Cuomo announced that all school districts in New York State will remain closed through May 15, 2020 as part of his extension of the statewide PAUSE to help protect the public against the spread of the COVID-19 virus. During this extended school closure, our District will continue all current practices and procedures related to our continuity of learning plan, child care for essential workers, and food distribution. We have gathered some resources to continue supporting parents during this time. Click on this <a href="https://www.smore.com/ft14p" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.smore.com/ft14p&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1587150478972000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEdNRm0CsOHHLY3pAFSRIcIoQsOBw">link to view the CCSD Family Newsletter</a>.</p></div>
